Generate QR code</font></h3><p style="font-size: 14px"><font data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">The payment method <b>qrCodeUrl </b>is returned for merchant who operates based on system which does not support internet browser hence cannot use the web-based ready-built UI provided by MoMo.</font></p><p style="font-size: 14px"><font data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">Merchant generates the QR code then displays it in merchant's custom UI (approved by MoMo).</font></p>" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;fillColor=#FFFFFF;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;arcSize=3;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="536" y="880" width="224" height="320" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-31" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-32" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-52"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-32" value="<h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font style="line-height: 140% ; font-size: 16px" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" color="#a50064">4.2. Redirect to MoMo web</font></h3><p style="font-size: 14px"><font data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">The payment method <b>payUrl&nbsp; &nbsp; </b>(default method) is returned for merchant who operates on website.</font></p><font style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">Merchant redirects user to MoMo website via this payUrl.&nbsp;This website automatically detects the platform in which merchant's website is running on to proceed accordingly.</font><font color="#ad246f"><b><br></b></font>" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;fillColor=#FFFFFF;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;arcSize=2;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="540" y="560" width="220" height="300" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-33" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-34" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-39"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-34" value="<h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font style="line-height: 140% ; font-size: 16px" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" color="#a50064">2. Request payment method</font></h3><p><font data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">Merchant system initiates an order containing order information associated with a unique orderId, then sends to MoMo for requesting the payment method most appropriate, along with the Merchant's credentials.</font></p>" style="text;html=1;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;arcSize=3;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="540" y="99" width="220" height="242" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-35" value="<p style="line-height: 130%"></p><h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font color="#a50064" style="font-size: 16px">8. Display payment result</font></h3><p><font style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px">Receive payment result, then display the result to user's acknowledgement.</font></p><p></p>" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;fillColor=#FFFFFF;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;arcSize=7;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="540" y="1620" width="220" height="114" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-36" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-37" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-24"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-37" value="<h3><font style="line-height: 140% ; font-size: 16px" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" color="#a50064">4.2.2. MoMo web on non-mobile device(s)</font></h3><p><font style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">If user is on desktop website (usually of PC, 2nd monitor of dual-screen POS device, some Kiosk devices), tablet or smartTV, the payUrl will redirect user to MoMo's payment gateway website which displays a QR code in pre-built UI.</font></p><font color="#ad246f"><b><br></b></font>" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;fillColor=#FFFFFF;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;arcSize=3;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="800" y="880" width="220" height="320" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-38" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-39" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-28"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-39" value="<p style="line-height: 140%"></p><h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font color="#a50064" style="font-size: 16px">3. Return payment method</font></h3><p><font style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">After validating the merchant authentication, respond with the requested payment method.</font></p><p></p>" style="text;html=1;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;fillColor=default;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;arcSize=3;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="800" y="99" width="220" height="242" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-40" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-41" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-26"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-41" value="<p style="line-height: 130%"></p><h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font color="#a50064" style="font-size: 16px">4.2.1. </font><font style="font-size: 16px" color="#99004d">MoMo</font><font color="#a50064" style="font-size: 16px"> web on mobile</font></h3><h3 style="font-size: 14px"><font style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: rgb(48 , 50 , 51) ; font-weight: normal ; line-height: 150%">If user is on a mobile device, the payUrl will redirect user to MoMo app. In case MoMo app hasn't been installed yet, payUrl will redirect user to app store for MoMo app installation.</span></font></h3><font color="#ad246f" style="font-size: 14px"><b><br></b></font><p></p>" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;fillColor=#FFFFFF;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;arcSize=4;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="1060" y="880" width="220" height="322" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-42" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-43" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-26"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-43" value="<p style="line-height: 100%"></p><h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font style="font-size: 16px" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" color="#a50064">4.1. Redirect to MoMo app</font></h3><p style="font-size: 14px"><font data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">The payment method <font style="font-weight: bold ; font-size: 14px">deeplink </font>or <font style="font-weight: bold ; font-size: 14px">deeplinkMiniApp&nbsp;</font>is returned for merchant who operates on mobile application.</font></p><p style="font-size: 14px"><font data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=calibri" style="line-height: 150% ; font-size: 14px" color="#303233">Merchant redirects user to MoMo app for them to confirm the payment. In case MoMo app hasn't been installed in user's mobile device, merchant should redirect user to app store for MoMo app installation.</font></p><p></p>" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#E5E5E5;fillColor=#FFFFFF;spacing=10;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=1;fontFamily=Roboto;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DRoboto;arcSize=3;" vertex="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21"> <mxGeometry x="1059" y="360" width="221" height="320" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-44" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#727272;" edge="1" parent="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-21" source="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-45" target="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-35"> <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> <mxCell id="68qwwxpgqxr8bHo_E7xc-45" value="<h3 style="font-size: 16px"><font color="#a50064" style="font-size: 16px">7.
